Example: (6x^4) - (5x^2) + 7 
Terms: (6x^4), (-5x^2), 7 
Coefficient: 6, -5, 7 
Degree: 4th, 2nd, 0
Leading Term: (6x^4)
Leading Coefficient: 6



Example: (3x^2) + 8 - 9x + (7x^5)
Terms: (7x^5), (3x^2), (-9x), 8
Coefficient: 7, 3, -9, 8
Degree: 5, 2, 1, 0
Leading Term: (7x^5)
Leading Coefficient: 7
Degree Polynomial: 5



Example: 7xy + (6x^2y) - 8 + (3x^2y^3) - (5xy^2)
Terms: (3x^2y^3) + (6x^2y) - (5xy^2) + 7xy - 8
Coefficient: 3, 6, -5, 7, -8
Degree: 5, 3, 3, 2, 0
Leading Term: (3x^2y^3)
Leading Coefficient: 3
Degree Polynomial: 5



