Section 5.7

In this section, we learn to recognize and apply specific multiplication results called the special products of polynomials.




(a^2) + (b^2) = (a + b)(a + b)

(a^2) - (b^2) = (a + b)(a - b)

(a + b)^2 = (a^2) + 2ab + (b^2)

(a - b)^2 = (a^2) - 2ab + (b^2)

(a^3) + (b^3) = (a + b)[(a^2) - ab + (b^2)]

(a^3) - (b^3) = (a - b)[(a^2) + ab + (b^2)]

[(x+2)^2] = 
(x+2)(x+2) = 
(x^2) + 2x + 2x + 4 = 
(x^2) + 4x + 4

([(x^2) - 1]^2) = 
[(x^2) - 1][(x^2) - 1] = 
(x^4) - (x^2) - (x^2) + 1 = 
(x^4) - (2x^2) + 1

(x-y)(x+y) = 
(x^2) + xy - xy - (y^2) = 
(x^2) - (y^2)

(2x+4y)(2x-4y) = 
(4x^2) - 8xy + 8xy - (16y^2) = 
(4x^2) - (16y^2)

[x - (y^2)(z)]^2 = 
[x - (y^2)(z)][x - (y^2)(z)] = 
(x^2) - (xy^2z) - (xy^2z) + (y^4z^2) = 
(x^2) - (2xy^2z) + (y^4z^2)

(2z + 9)^2 = 
(2z + 9)(2z + 9) = 
(4x^2) + 18z + 18z + 81 = 
(4x^2) + 36z + 81 

[(x+1) - 4][(x+1) + 4] = 
[x - 3][x + 5] =
(x^2) + 5x - 3x - 15 =
(x^2) + 2x - 15

Quick Reference: (a^2) - (b^2) = (a + b)(a - b)

(x^2) - 16 =
(x + 4)(x - 4)

(x^2) - 49 =
(x + 7)(x - 7)

(25x^2) - 64 =
(5x + 8)(5x - 8)

(64x^2) - (121y^2) = 
(8x + 11y)(8x - 11y)



Quick Reference: (a^2) + 2ab + (b^2) = (a + b)^2 

(x^2) + 10x + 25 = 
(a^2) = (x^2)
a = x 
(b^2) = 25
b = 5

(x + 5)^2



