[(2x - 3)(2x - 3)(2x - 3)] =
[(4x^2) - 6x - 6x + 9](2x - 3) = 
[(4x^2) - 12x + 9](2x - 3) = 
(8x^3) - (12x^2) - 24x + 36x + 18x - 27 =
(8x^3) - (36x^2) + 54x - 27 






